markets.title: How long will luther (with sza) be #1?
markets.subtitle: More than 19 weeks
markets.rules_primary: If luther (with sza) has had the #1 spot on the Billboard Hot 100 for more than 19 consecutive weeks, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: If this event occurs, or the streak ends, the market will close the following 10am ET. This market specifically encompasses the first streak luther (with sza) holds.
markets.early_close_condition: If this event occurs, or the streak ends (if the market is about the streak, not the total number of weeks) the market will close the following 10am ET.
